attributes.review: When I downloaded this app I was hoping to get more information on Trump‚Äôs campaign. What I got instead was a pile of poo delivered straight to my door. Yes. A box with dog poo in it showed up at my front door the second I hit the download button. On it was a note that said ‚ÄúThanks for downloading my app, idiot. I love u - Donald Trumpüíã‚Äù with the official White House seal. When I actually got into the app it kept crashing and/or taking me to YouTube videos from 2014. Now my phone won‚Äôt stop playing Thrift Shop by Macklemore. I literally can‚Äôt get it to stop. Macklemore‚Äôs hit song ‚ÄúThrift Shop‚Äù is blaring throughout my house constantly, as my phone has somehow become connected to every one of my speakers. The song, which describes a trip taken by musical artist Macklemore to an open-air market in Seattle, has now been playing on a loop for a solid 2 hours and 7 minutes. The hit single is on a volume so high that every window in my house broke. Does anyone know how to fix this????
